data.actual_result: The console is spammed with errors and you can't record keybind.
data.expected_result: It should change record your keybind so it can save and no errors should occur
data.short_description: Attempting to change keybind for the overlay will cause error spam in the console and won't change the keybind
data.steps_to_repro: - Go to user settings > overlay - Click record so you can map a new keybind - Observe it not recording the keybind and observe errors in console
